<LI><LINK to="../probstat/index.html">@{<E>Probability and Statistics</E>@}</LINK> </LI>
</OL>
baigulote kI Achhe, kena likhechhi, ityAdi gurugambhIr prashne yAoyAr Age sahaj kayekTA prashner jabAb diye neoyA yAk. 
<UL><LI>baigulo kArA bAr karechhe?  shara.t buk hAus (orafe @{<E>Levant Publishers</E>@}).</LI>
<LI>kothAy pAoyA yAy? kalej sTrITe  shara.t buk hAuser dokAne (kalej sTrIT Ar
 mahAt+mA gAndhI roDer krasi.n-e). kalej sTrITer anya kichhu dokAneo (yeman @{<E>National</E>@}
 bA @{<E>International</E>@}) pAoyA yAoyA uchit. baiyer nAm, shara.t buk hAus eba.n lekhaker nAm
 (arNab chak+rabar+tI) balle kalkAtAr yekono baiyer dokAnai Aniye dite pAre. tabe shara.t buk
 hAuser bejAy kaRAkaRi, nagad paysA nA dile kono baiyer dokAn~dArke bai dey nA. tAi ``baiTA ekTu
 AnAben to dAdA, kenA yAy kinA bhAbba''-jAtIya anurodh karle ApnAr baiyer dokAn~dAr ApnAke saTAn
 bale debe ye, oi baiTA pAoyA yAchchhe nA.</LI>
<LI>@{<E>Online</E>@}-e pAoyA yAy nA? h,nyA yAy. 
<LINK to="http://www.saratbookhouse.com">shara.t buk hAuser oyebsAiTe</LINK> giye okhAnkAr 
@{<E>search</E>@}-e AmAr nAm diye kh,nujle bibhinna baiyer pAtAy niye yAbe. sekhAn theke baigulo kenA yAbe. 
kono kArD lAgbe nA, @{<E>cash on delivery.</E>@} tabe @{<E>shipping charge</E>@} nebe ek sha TAkA, ye kono jAygAr janyai. 
<P/>
@{<E>Amazon, Flipkart</E>@} ityAdi jAygAteo mAjhe mAjhe AmAr baigulo dekhA dey, kintu
 tArparei fer miliye yAy.</LI>
</UL>
<HEAD2>bA.nlAy-bojhAno-i.nrAji-bai mAne?</HEAD2>
bijnAner ye kono shAkhAi i.nrAjite shekhAi bhAlo. kintu du.Hkher biSay ye, i.nrAji bhASATA yataTA saRagaRa hale 
tAr mAdhyame bijnAn Ayatta karA yAy, tataTA shekhAr suYog khub kam bA\ngAlIr bhAgyei joTe. syuT-buT-TAi-manDita 
i.nlish miDiyame paRA bangasantAner abhAb nei, kintu tAder daxatA k,nAdh @{<E>shrug</E>@} karA Ar
 biliti kAydAr hAsi hAsAte yataTA, i.nrAji jnAner gabhIratAy tatTA nay.    tAder doS dite pAri nA, hAjAr hok 
chab+bish ghan+TAr  madhye mAtra kayek ghan+TA ekTA biliti bhASAr khAnik bukni shune to Ar 
rAtArAti se bhASAy daxa haye oThA yAy nA, bisheSata.H se buknigulor u.tsa  yekhAne nitAnta deshI mAnuSjan, 
yAder nijederai oi bhASAy teman kono daxatA nei. 
<P/>
satyaTA ei ye, bA\ngAlIrA bA.nlATAi bhAlo bojhe. 
rAshiyAnrA yeman bhAlo bojhe rushbhASA, bA iTAliyAnrA tAder desher bhASA. tabe tAder sange AmAder pradhAn pArthakya ei ye, 
tArA sei sahaj satyaTA kabul karte lajjA pAy nA, AmrA pAi. 
<P/>
bijnAnke bA\ngAlIr kAchhe p,n\ouchhe debAr pathe tAi bhASAr samasyATA anas+wIkArYa. tAr ekTA @{<E>"</E>@}samAdhAn@{<E>"</E>@} 
bhebechhilen satyen bos. t,nAr mane hayechhila ye, i.nrAjI @{<E>technical term</E>@}-guloi yata naSTer goRA. 
oguloke bA.nlAy tar+jamA kare fellei bijnAn ekebAre pAkA AmTir mata bA\ngAlI hAte Tup kare khase paRbe.  
onAr ei hAsyakar parikal+panAy abashya hAsir cheye kAnnAr  kAraNai beshI ghaTechhe. guchchher bA.nlA paribhASA 
t\oirI haoyA (yegulo i.nrAjir cheyeo anek beshI aparichita, eba.n yAder kono @{<E>standard</E>@} nei) eba.n
sei janya niYuk+ta kichhu @{<E>"</E>@}panDit@{<E>"</E>@}-er pakeTbharA chhARA tAr dwArA kono fal
 hay ni. ekTA kufal hayechhe abashya. mAnuSer mane ei dhAraNA Arao baddhamUl hayechhe ye, bA.nlAr mAdhyame 
bijnAn shekhAr cheSTAr mata abAs+tab Ar kichhui hate pAre nA. sutarA.n ekhan  adhikA.nsha
 bA\ngAlIr bishwAs  ye, 
ekai sange i.nrAjI eba.n i.nrAjI byabahAr kare bijnAn duii shikhe felte hay. adhikA.nshai sei durUha karme 
xAnta diye bale--bijnAn-TijnAn bhAi AmAder chhelemeyeder janye nay. Arek dal
i.nrAjite bijnAn mukhastha kare mere debAr janya AprAN cheSTA chAlAy 
(eba.n sei sange bA.nlAy bijnAn shixAr mAn uttarottar 
nAmiye Ane). erai madhye b,neche yAy seisab bhAgyabAnerA yAder abhibhAbak chhoTobelAtei santAnke 
saYatne i.nrAji shixA diye nen, prathAgata shixAr toyAk+kA nA rekhe. eder sa.nkhyA atyantai kam. 
athacha kArorai mAthAy ei ati sahaj kthATA Ase nA ye, ekbAr bhebe dekhi duniyAr anyatra
 chhelemeyerA kIkare bijnAn shikhchhe.  i.nlanD Ar AmerikA bAd dile bAki kothAoi to Ar i.nrAjI
 mAtrribhASA nay, bA i.nlish miDiyam skulerao chhaRAchhaRi nei. tArA kI sabAi satyen boser mata
 nij nija bhASAy guchchher paribhASA bAnAchchhe? nA, tArA nijeder bhASAtei paRAshonA karchhe,
 @{<E>technical term</E>@}-gulo i.nrAjItei rekhe.   sei ati sahaj buddhir kAjTAi karAr cheSTA karechhi AmAr baigulote. 
ekhAne @{<E>definition, theorem</E>@} eman ki @{<E>exercise, example</E>@}eba.n tAder samAdhAnao i.nrAjite, khAli bojhAnogulo 
bA.nlAy. ekTA udAharaN dekhAi--dharA yAk ekTA i.nrAji baite likhechhe 
<Q>@{<E>At this point we would like to remind the reader that if we differentiate <M>\sin x</M> then 
we get <M>\cos x.</M></E>@}  </Q>
i.nrAjite k,nAchA a.nker chhAtrachhAtrIr  kAchhe kintu ekhAne
@{<M>\sin x</M>@} bA @{<M>\cos x </M>@}bA @{<E>differentiate</E>@} 
karA konoTAi kaThin Thekbe nA. kaThin Thekbe i.nrAji bAkyaTAr kAThAmo. sei kaSTa dUr karAr janya 
@{<E>differentiate</E>@} karAke abakalan bA oi rakam kono bid.hghuTe bA.nlA diye tar+jamA kare lAbh nei, lekhAr darkAr--
<Q>eikhAne ekbAr mane kariye dii ye, @{<M>\sin x</M>@}-ke @{<E>differentiate</E>@} karle @{<M>\cos x</M>@} hay.</Q>
AmAr baite Ami Thik seTAi karechhi. 

<HEAD2>baigulo kAder janya?</HEAD2>
sahaj uttar hala--yArA paRe upakrrita habe tAder janya.  tabe lekhAr samaye ekTA bisheS dharaNer pAThaker kathA mane rekhei 
baigulo lekhA, yArA bhabiSya.t prajanmer shikkhak hate yAchchhe.  shixak balte Ami balchhi tAder kathA yArA 
satyai chhAtrader shixakatAr kAje yuk+ta thAken. ThAnDA ghare base palisi t\oirI karneoyAlAder kathA nay. 
bA bejAy nAmkarA ins.hTiTiuTer bejAy moTA moTA mAine pAoyA sei sab prafesar~der kathAo nay, yArA baRojor 
goTA tirishek chhAtra sAm~lAtei himsim kheye afis paliTik+sei samay byay karen beshI. Ami balchhi tAder
kathA yAder hAt diye prachur chhAtra beroy, y,nArA kochi.n klAser goyAl sAm~lAn, hayto pAr+T-TAime paRAn, 
ki.nbA sref prAibheTei paRAn. kintu satyai y,nArA paRAn. e,nder paRAnor mAn khub u,nchu hay nA,  kAraN seTA 
sambhab nay. kintu yadi sei mAn sAmAnyao unnata karA yAy, tabe tAr prabhAb paRe bahu chhAtrader upare.  
AmAr bai paRe lokjan dh,nA kare rAtArAti a.nke panDit haye yAbe, eman ra\ngIn kalpanA kari nA. 
@{<E>Math Olympiad</E>@} ``kryAk'' karbAr hAtuRi  eisab baite nei. AmAr uddeshya khAli eiTA
 sAbyas+ta karA ye,  
a.nka jinisTA nIras nay, eba.n seTA upabhog karAr janya prachanDa buddhimAn bA i.nrAjIte
 bhISaN os+tAd hate hay nA. 

<HEAD2>baigulor b\oishiSTya</HEAD2>
<OL>
<LI>egulo sAdhAraN chhAtrader janya lekhA @{<E>textbook.</E>@} silebAs dhare lekhA. gata dash bachharer prashner
samAdhAn-suddha. arthA.t parIxA pAsher yAbatIya upakaraNer byabasthA Achhe ete. kAraN AmAder
 silebAs o parIxAbyabasthA yatai jaghanya hok, or upasthiti anas+wIkArYa. muSTimeya ye kayjan 
bhAgyabAn  @{<E>ISI, IIT</E>@} ityAdi jAygAy 
Dhuke paRte perechhe, tArA nirApad dUratwe theke  mAndhAtA Amaler silebAsgulo dekhe nAk s,niTkote 
pAre. kintu yAderke bAdhya hayei sei mAndhAtA Amaler andhakUpe pache marte hay, tAder madhya thekei 
bhabiSya.t prajanmer shixakrA beroy beshI. silebAs~ke hAjAr ghrriNA karleo  agrAhya karA sambhab nay tAder paxe. 
</LI>
<LI>baigulote a.nka upasthApanAr mAn AmAr jAnA kono @{<E>international standard</E>@} baiyer cheye kam nay. 
silebAs dhare lekhA mAne ei nay ye, silebAsei sImAbaddha. silebAsTA yena khAnAkhande  paripUrNa ekTA 
ebRokhebRo rAs+tA. silebAs anuYAyI lekhA bai balte AmrA bhebe nii yena ekTA chhyAkrA gARI yeTA sei 
rAs+tAr upar diye chhAtrader hiR.h hiR.h kare chh,nyAchRAte chh,nyAchRAte Tene niye yAbe. Ar Adarsha 
bai balte bujhi ekTA dur+dAnta gARi yeTAy chaRlei jIban juRiye yAy, khAli seTA gantabye
 p,n\ouchhoy nA ei yA du.Hkha. yArA gARi chaRe khAli hAoyA khAoyAr uddeshye,  se gARi
 kebal tAderai janya.  
AmAr baigulote Ami  oi hAoyA khAoyAr ArAmer gARigulokei jutechhi 
silebAser rAs+tAy, tAr janya khAnAkhanda yekhAne yA merAmat kare neoyAr darkAr kare niyechhi.
ei sab bai theke shikhe yena parIxAy nambar pete asubidhA nA hay, se dike bisheS najar diyechhi. </LI>
<LI>prachur chhabi e,nkechhi baigulote. deshI baigulor to kathAi nei, bideshI a.nka baiteo
 chhabir byabahAr khubai kam. athacha kono natun dhAraNA bojhAte chhabir upaYogitA aparisIm.  </LI>
</OL>

<HEAD2>AgrahI?</HEAD2>

ei baigulo lekhAr kAjTAke mane karA yete pAre ekTA baRa  projek+Ter a.nsha. ye kono baRa projek+Tei AgrahI 
mAnuSjaner samAbesh kAmya. keu yadi ei projek+Te sAmil hate chAn tabe nIcher panthAgulo bhebe dekhte pAren@{<E>:</E>@}
<UL>
<LI>baigulor sambandhe aparke jAnAte pAren. yadi jAnAn tabe dayA kare yena ederke @{<E>"</E>@}mahAn
 Adarsher@{<E>"</E>@} nidarshan hisebe bijnApita karben nA. AmAder deshe mahAn Adarsher eta chhaRAchhaRi ye, 
oi jAtIya kathA shunlei loke bhanDAmi bale mane kare. @{<E>"</E>@}ei baigulo paRe sahaje parIxAy
 nambar pAoyA yAy@{<E>"</E>@} ballei yeTuku kAj habAr habe. </LI>
<LI>bA.nlA bhASAy bijnAn mAnei ye kichhu @{<E>technical term</E>@}-er bA.nlA tar+jamAr A,ntlAmi  nay, tAr
udAharaN hisebe ei baigulor ul+lekh karA. 
 </LI>
<LI>bhArater anyAnya bhASAte ei baigulor anubAde sAhAYya karA. dil+lIr ekjan sahrriday prafesar   itimadhyei 
hindI anubAder kAje kichhu dUr agrasar hayechhen. erakam anubAd karbAr janya--
<UL>
<LI>bA.nlA jAnAr prayojan nei. Ami AmAr baiTA mukhe mukhe i.nrAjI kare rekar+D kare in+TAr~neTer
 mAdhyame pAThiye diye thAki. puro baiyer kAThAmoTAo imel kare pAThiye dii, yAr madhye i.nrAjI
 a.nshagulo lekhAi thAke. bA.nlAgulor jAygAy khAli @{<E>...</E>@} thAke, segulo AmAr rekar+Di.n
 shune pUraN kare dilei hala.</LI>
<LI>bibhinna bhAratIya bhASA kampiuTAre TAip karAr janya @{<E>Google</E>@}-ei byabsthA Achhe. tA
 diyei kAj chale yAy. kono kichhu @{<E>install</E>@} karte hay nA.</LI>
<LI>Ar h,nyA, Ami kintu ei kAjer janya paysA dite pArba nA. tabe yA lekhA habe seTA anubAdaker sam+patti.</LI>
<LI> kAjTA samasApexa haleo kono dharAb,nAdhA samaysImA nei. khAnik dUr giye chheRe dileo Apatti nei. 
anubAder byApArTA puroTAi parIxAmUlak. </LI>
</UL>
 </LI>
</UL> 
</NOTE>
